Invocation Name: c. m. i.
des:
With the "CMI Appointment Monitor for Dentech" you can: 
 Get information about your or the offices appointment count
 Get your appointment count status (How many appointments remaining / completed appointments)
 Get Information about your next scheduled appointment.
 Print any of your appointments Router (Patient Care Form) 

You can also move appointments to their current phase (Checked In, In Treatment, and Checked out)

This skill requires that the (Check-Me-In software) has been integrated with your Practice Management System.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
